{"tid":1533574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要求中央交代: 究竟林鄭有冇交報告比中央，爭取過5大訴求?","createTime":"2019-09-02T18:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:51:51.000Z","uid":235512,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2842f2cec5092b379760fb046192b0c5aaae103d","tid":1533574,"uid":235512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T18:05:22.000Z","msg":"嘩，路透社咁大反應，咁驚港人矛頭指向中央既?<br />\n<br />\n咁中央應該出嚟解下話啦。呢單新聞點做假法?<br />\n<br />\n1. 係林鄭冇寫過或交過報告? <br />\n<br />\n2. 林鄭寫過報告，但冇提意過答應5大訴求?<br />\n<br />\n3. 林鄭寫咗交比港澳辦，中央知唔知情? 唔知情，所以中央冇拒絕過5大訴求?<br />\n<br />\n4. 中央知情，但答應過5大訴求?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透社引消息：林鄭曾交報告　北京下令拒絕五大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/369777/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9B%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F369777%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=399be316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/369777/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9B%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82</a><br />\n<br />\n環時：路透社編造謠言挑撥離間　煽動示威者對抗中央<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/370030/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%92%B